{"tid":725079,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[影你大頭]女警手持超詳細表格　疑用作點人數　現身警總旁行人天橋","createTime":"2018-07-01T12:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T10:22:09.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f6dfc7d137c667c4b81aa9377881e94fffb32ded","tid":725079,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T12:50:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180701/s00001/1530445026785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180701%2Fs00001%2F1530445026785&d=M8uY2vHiIDNZRzycqwIdgx4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=f0beaafb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180701%2Fs00001%2F1530445026785&h=884c183f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180701/s00001/1530445026785</a><br />\n<br />\n民陣在七一遊行將結束時，宣布約有5萬人參與遊行。《明報》記者下午在灣仔警察總部旁的軍器廠街天橋，發現有警員手持極為詳細的表格，相信用作統計遊行人數。警方其後表示，遊行高峰期有約9800人參與。<br />\n<br />\n拿着該份表格的女警身上有警察委任證。從《明報》記者拍攝的照片可見，表格上印有今日日期，並寫有遊行主辦組織民陣的名字。表格第一欄列出由下午12時半開始計算的時間，每15分鐘一列，一直列至表格底部。<br />\n<br />\n表格並列出疑是不同觀察點的代號，其中「中央」、「波橋」、「軍橋」及「海富」，相信分別代表遊行路線途經的中央圖書館、波斯富街天橋、軍器廠街天橋及海富中心。<br />\n<br />\n軍器廠街天橋上亦有穿上「港大民研」背心的統計員，及身穿「警察」背心的警員，拍攝及統計遊行人數。另在港大民研統計員身旁，有約6名穿便服的人，他們以兩部同一牌子的相機拍攝遊行人士，另有人將錄影的片段即時存入電腦，截圖後即場「數人頭」。該6名人士沒有穿上制服或展示任何委任證，但《明報》記者曾目睹前述手持表格的女警與他們談話。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180701/s00001/57fefcc7d998f02dc69cc0fd9ca1a16a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180701%2Fs00001%2F57fefcc7d998f02dc69cc0fd9ca1a16a.jpg&h=c560e069&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180701/s00001/57feb1af0fa307aa607201f1f66a1a03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180701%2Fs00001%2F57feb1af0fa307aa607201f1f66a1a03.jpg&h=3148c58e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《明報》記者在軍器廠街天橋，拍得一名女警手持一份內容詳細的表格，懷疑用作點算遊行人數。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180701/s00001/57fe6cba01bc9b1dd6e403b90b11351b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180701%2Fs00001%2F57fe6cba01bc9b1dd6e403b90b11351b.jpg&h=f533f529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多名身分不明的人，在軍器廠街天橋拍攝遊行人士，並即時存入電腦。他們沒有穿上制服，亦無展示任何委任證，但《明報》記者曾目睹手持表格的女警與他們交談。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180701/s00001/57fe4a4207118d3c7a8848a5b1daa63d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180701%2Fs00001%2F57fe4a4207118d3c7a8848a5b1daa63d.jpg&h=982899c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n軍器廠街天橋上亦有穿上「港大民研」背心的統計員（照片後方），旁邊有約6人以相機拍攝遊行情況，並即時存入電腦，該6人未有穿上任何制服或展示任何委任證，《明報》記者曾目睹他們與手持表格的女警交談。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180701/s00001/57fe8fe0084ca8f631d59995d769f3c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180701%2Fs00001%2F57fe8fe0084ca8f631d59995d769f3c9.jpg&h=71763332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有穿上警察背心的警員，在軍器廠街天橋拍攝遊行情況。"},{"pid":"c56ac398948b5a23636d23e9b91a9cf511846430","tid":725079,"uid":11890,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T12:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/205808_1af041a251cd41a1ad64c9955813afd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F205808_1af041a251cd41a1ad64c9955813afd5.png&h=889a9461&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"480a774e0bbca3ee7373c29706af3f8948e740e8","tid":725079,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T13:05:17.000Z","msg":"遲早到香港玩大陸個濕鳩信用制，加上之前資料外洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7159b4302e626c7717d035deb562605aae7736","tid":725079,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T13:19:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"